{"tid":2415343,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"夏博義拒辭大律師公會主席　湯家驊：感到失望 公會與北京關係沒好轉機會","createTime":"2021-02-20T07:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:34:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2b0aabf82bf3ac4bdc2375ce74ad1f058dd83d8d","tid":2415343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"資深大律師夏博義就任大律師公會主席一個月。他接受本台專訪時稱，並無隱瞞政治背景，不會辭職。大律師公會前主席資深大律師湯家驊表示，對夏博義的說法感到失望，又擔心如果他不離任，公會與北京的關係會更差。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：「社會觀感最差的感覺，第一是影響大律師公會的獨立性，第二是對於他可否獨立處理香港司法制度的問題。沒有提到如何與北京重新建立好伙伴關係、如何帶領業界在大灣區發展業務，他似乎完全不明白社會對他的質疑，看不到公會與北京的關係會有任何好轉的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424715&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=7c18e363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424715&h=3e31f1d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424715</a>"},{"pid":"8ae1bf4036c247f5512275ab9db2013fa03f0ce5","tid":2415343,"uid":76804,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"點解要同北京關係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e4076a1d75f5d49e8183bb477bfaebc8d26990","tid":2415343,"uid":224857,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc0cca4d9078c2ec7b84ff6a05e9a0cd0b76b46","tid":2415343,"uid":127575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"美國有11哥<br />\n香港都有11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f688f0a08724bf2a5f5128ee3f06f74b61f25313","tid":2415343,"uid":249608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"dll